<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Hi&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName}!</span></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Remember learning about the power of your political voice during the Bite The Ballot session on NCS?</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><img src="http://jmu-journalism.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/BTB.jpg"></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Well now The Challenge Society is working in partnership with Bite The Ballot (BTB) to offer 10 NCS graduates from West London the opportunity to become an accredited Changemaker.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b>What does it involve?</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Changemakers will participate in three main activities between February and May 2016:</div><div><ul><li><font face="arial"><b>Participation: </b>Help BTB with their National Voter Registration Drive in early February.</font></li><li><font face="arial"><b>Online and Offline Social Action: </b>Bring your local communities together to talk about the big issues.</font></li><li><font face="arial"><b>Accountability and Decision Making: </b>Organise and take part in your local 'Leaders Live' event, getting the chance to question and hold to account the people who make the big decisions where you live.</font></li></ul><div><font face="arial"><b>Why should I take part?</b></font></div></div><div><font face="arial"><b><br></b></font></div><div><font face="arial">You'll become an accredited Changemaker, with the opportunity to train future generations of young people on everything you've learned.</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">You'll learn loads of new skills, including campaign planning, effective social media, political advocacy, fundraising, and so many more!</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">You'll get VIP access to a range of future opportunities with BTB, including travel, international training and employment.</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><b>How do I apply?</b>&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Fill in <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1POYwqhZ1DX_8KtFE_d5mc2UjVKcY045jXZ_CdNi5Ik4/viewform?usp=send_form">this form</a>&nbsp;and we'll be in touch if you're successful. The deadline for applying is <b>16:00</b> on <b>Friday 11th December</b>.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Click <a href="http://bitetheballot.co.uk/curriculum/">here</a> for more information about the programme. We look forward to hearing from you!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">The Challenge Society</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div>]]></td>
</tr>
